            . I cannot say I know the prisoner or evidence. I was robbed the same night, the 11th of January, in <placeName id="t17700221-6-crimeloc30">Stepney-fields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17700221-6-crimeloc30" type="placeName" value="Stepney-fields"></interp>
