            1st.) He was a third time indicted for <rs id="t17700221-6-off32" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17700221-6-off32" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17700221-6-off32" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               making an assault on 
                     
                        <persName id="t17700221-6-victim101" type="victimName">
                           Edward
                            Smith
                        <interp inst="t17700221-6-victim101" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
